Makro has unveiled its Cyber Monday 2018 sale, which is valid for today only. The deals will be available online only, with “big savings on selected products across the hi-tech, multimedia, outdoor, and appliance categories”. Makro said stocks are limited, and that orders will take 7-10 days to fulfil. A selection of great tech deals from Makro’s Cyber Monday sale are shown below. Click the images to enlarge them. You can view all the deals here.     